### Steps for Classic Dart:
1. Start with a rectangle (FileText)
2. Fold lengthwise (MoveVertical)
3. Fold corners in (Triangle)
4. Fold top down (ArrowDown)
5. Fold corners again (Minimize2)
6. Fold in half (BookOpen)
7. Make the wings (Wind)
8. Launch it! (Send - green card)

### Steps for The Glider:
1. Start with a rectangle (FileText)
2. Fold lengthwise (MoveVertical)
3. Fold corners to center (Triangle)
4. Fold peak down (ArrowDown)
5. Fold corners again (Minimize2)
6. Lock the fold (Triangle)
7. Fold backwards (BookOpen)
8. Create wings (Wind)
9. Launch it! (Send - green card)

