## üé≠ ANIMATIONS & INTERACTIONS

### Motion Library
- Package: `motion/react` (formerly framer-motion)
- Version: ^12.23.25

### Common Animation Patterns
```javascript
// Fade in + slide up
initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 20 }}
animate={{ opacity: 1, y: 0 }}

// Scale entrance
initial={{ scale: 0.8 }}
animate={{ scale: 1 }}

// Breathing effect
animate={{ scale: [1, 1.1, 1] }}
transition={{ repeat: Infinity, duration: 2, ease: "easeInOut" }}

// Staggered children
transition={{ delay: index * 0.1 }}

// Card interactions
whileHover={{ scale: 1.02 }}
whileTap={{ scale: 0.98 }}
```

### Transitions
- Default duration: 0.2-0.3s
- Ease: Usually default or easeInOut
- Delays: Staggered by 0.05-0.1s increments

